qcom-pal (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Introduced new API for SPR shared memory management.
  * Enabled usage of versioned shared objects for dlopen operations.
  * Added support for retrieving latency using DSP calls.
  * Updated Debian packaging with audio node rules and metadata.
  * Fixed compilation and memory handling issues.

